{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778982107837,"sessionID":"ses_1cc676134ffe2LibXsrsp2MYr0","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_sLHk2abh4D9fBFg23tRVCppq","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/__issue_context__.json","offset":1,"limit":400},"output":"<path>/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/__issue_context__.json</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: {\n2:   \"body\": \"This term has no enzyme xref:\\n\\nid: GO:0045550\\nname: geranylgeranyl reductase activity\\nnamespace: molecular_function\\ndef: \\\"Catalysis of the formation of phytyl group from the stepwise reduction of a geranylgeranyl group.\\\" [PMID:9492312]\\nis_a: GO:0016491 ! oxidoreductase activity\\n\\nPMID:9492312 abstract says:\\n\\\"Geranylgeranyl reductase expressed in Escherichia coli sequentially catalyzes the reduction of geranylgeranyl-chlorophyll a into phytyl-chlorophyll a as well as the reduction of free geranylgeranyl diphosphate into phytyl diphosphate.\\\"\\n\\nBoth these reactions are covered by EC:1.3.1.83, whose entry says:\\nReaction catalysed: phytyl diphosphate + 3 NADP(+) = geranylgeranyl diphosphate + 3 NADPH + 3 H(+)\\nComments: This enzyme also acts on geranylgeranyl-chlorophyll a.\\n\\nThis is consistent with the MetaCyc entry for this gene (also attributed to PMID:9492312): https://metacyc.org/gene?orgid=META&id=AT1G74470-MONOMER#REFS\\n\\nSo:\\n- [x] GO:0045550 should be obsoleted and replaced with GO:0102067:\\n\\nid: GO:0102067\\nname: geranylgeranyl diphosphate reductase activity\\nnamespace: molecular_function\\ndef: \\\"Catalysis of the reaction: (E)-3,7,11,15-tetramethylhexadec-2-en-1-yl diphosphate + 3 NADP = 2-trans,6-trans,10-trans-geranylgeranyl diphosphate + 3 NADPH + 3 H+.\\\" [EC:1.3.1.83, GOC:pz]\\nxref: EC:1.3.1.83 {source=\\\"skos:exactMatch\\\"}\\nxref: MetaCyc:RXN-10625\\nxref: RHEA:26229 {source=\\\"skos:exactMatch\\\"}\\nis_a: GO:0016628 ! oxidoreductase activity, acting on the CH-CH group of donors, NAD or NADP as acceptor\\nproperty_value: term_tracker_item \\\"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/30193\\\" xsd:anyURI\\n\\n\\nThere are only 3 annotations to GO:0045550 geranylgeranyl reductase activity:\\n- human [AKR1C3](https://amigo.geneontology.org/amigo/gene_product/UniProtKB:P42330) by UP\\n- human [AKR1B10](https://amigo.geneontology.org/amigo/gene_product/UniProtKB:O60218) by UP\\n- Arabidopsis [CHLP](https://amigo.geneontology.org/amigo/gene_pr... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n3:   \"comments\": [\n4:     {\n5:       \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAkAHws8AAAABAoTt7g\",\n6:       \"author\": {\n7:         \"login\": \"raymond91125\"\n8:       },\n9:       \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n10:       \"body\": \"@dragon-ai-agent please update GO:0102067 definition according to sjm41 comments. Do not close this ticket. Obsoletion is to be completed later.\",\n11:       \"createdAt\": \"2026-04-28T16:34:47Z\",\n12:       \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n13:       \"isMinimized\": false,\n14:       \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n15:       \"reactionGroups\": [\n16:         {\n17:           \"content\": \"EYES\",\n18:           \"users\": {\n19:             \"totalCount\": 1\n20:           }\n21:         }\n22:       ],\n23:       \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31963#issuecomment-4337233390\",\n24:       \"viewerDidAuthor\": false\n25:     },\n26:     {\n27:       \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAkAHws8AAAABAoT3Qg\",\n28:       \"author\": {\n29:         \"login\": \"dragon-ai-agent\"\n30:       },\n31:       \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n32:       \"body\": \"🤖 Working on it...\\n\\nFollow along: [View workflow run](https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/actions/runs/25065339565)\\n\\n*— @dragon-ai-agent*\",\n33:       \"createdAt\": \"2026-04-28T16:35:11Z\",\n34:       \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n35:       \"isMinimized\": false,\n36:       \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n37:       \"reactionGroups\": [],\n38: