{"type":"text","timestamp":1778982115693,"sessionID":"ses_1cc676134ffe2LibXsrsp2MYr0","part":{"id":"prt_e3398c9460013AGjEtcEEM7YZC","messageID":"msg_e3398bd4c001ttgk3cg1rnyurc","sessionID":"ses_1cc676134ffe2LibXsrsp2MYr0","type":"text","text":"The issue scope changed in comments: do not obsolete yet; update `GO:0102067`'s definition to reflect the substrate breadth discussed in the issue. Next I’m checking the current term state, pattern guidance, and baseline validation status.","time":{"start":1778982111558,"end":1778982115691}}}
