ccurs in three steps.\n-   Which order the three double bonds are reduced is not known.\n\nCross-references\n\nRhea expert-curated reactions\n\n[1.3.1.83](https://www.rhea-db.org/rhea?query=ec%3A1.3.1.83)\n\nExplorEnz\n\n[1.3.1.83](http://www.enzyme-database.org/query.php?ec=1.3.1.83)\n\nIUBMB Enzyme Nomenclature\n\n[1.3.1.83](https://www.qmul.ac.uk/sbcs/iubmb/enzyme/EC1/3/1/83.html)\n\nUniProtKB/Swiss-Prot\n\n[P26172](https://www.uniprot.org/uniprot/P26172), BCHP\\_RHOCB\n\n[Q9CA67](https://www.uniprot.org/uniprot/Q9CA67), CHLP\\_ARATH\n\n[Q6Z2T6](https://www.uniprot.org/uniprot/Q6Z2T6), CHLP\\_ORYSJ\n\n[Q55087](https://www.uniprot.org/uniprot/Q55087), CHLP\\_SYNY3\n\n[Q9ZS34](https://www.uniprot.org/uniprot/Q9ZS34), CHLP\\_TOBAC\n\nBRENDA\n\n[1.3.1.83](http://www.brenda-enzymes.org/enzyme.php?ecno=1.3.1.83)\n\nMetaCyc\n\n[1.3.1.83](https://biocyc.org/META/NEW-IMAGE?type=EC-NUMBER&object=EC-1.3.1.83)\n\nKEGG Ligand Database for Enzyme Nomenclature\n\n[1.3.1.83](http://www.genome.ad.jp/dbget-bin/www_bget?ec:1.3.1.83)\n\nEC2PDB\n\n[1.3.1.83](https://www.ebi.ac.uk/thornton-srv/databases/cgi-bin/enzymes/GetPage.pl?ec_number=1.3.1.83)\n\nMEDLINE\n\n[Find literature relating to 1.3.1.83](https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/query.fcgi?cmd=PureSearch&db=PubMed&details_term=1.3.1.83[EC/RN%20Number])\n\n  \n[View entry in original ENZYME format](/cgi-bin/enzyme/get-enzyme-entry?1.3.1.83)  \n[View entry in raw text format (no links)](/EC/1.3.1.83.txt)  \n\n[All UniProtKB/Swiss-Prot entries referenced in this entry](https://www.uniprot.org/uniprotkb?query=\\(ec:1.3.1.83\\)%20AND%20\\(reviewed:true\\)), with possibility to download in different formats, align etc.\n\nAll [ENZYME](/EC/1.3.1.-) / [UniProtKB/Swiss-Prot](https://www.uniprot.org/uniprotkb?query=\\(ec:1.3.1.-\\)%20AND%20\\(reviewed:true\\)) entries corresponding to 1.3.1.-  \nAll [ENZYME](/EC/1.3.-.-) / [UniProtKB/Swiss-Prot](https://www.uniprot.org/uniprotkb?query=\\(ec:1.3.-.-\\)%20AND%20\\(reviewed:true\\)) entrie