{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778982572823,"sessionID":"ses_1cc676134ffe2LibXsrsp2MYr0","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_xA5NSIqoPSHtbFJ4TQBGxeRP","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/references_cache/PMID_9492312.md","offset":1,"limit":220},"output":"<path>/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/references_cache/PMID_9492312.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: ---\n2: reference_id: PMID:9492312\n3: title: Metabolic compartmentation of plastid prenyllipid biosynthesis--evidence for the involvement of a multifunctional geranylgeranyl reductase.\n4: authors:\n5: - Keller Y\n6: - Bouvier F\n7: - \"d'Harlingue A\"\n8: - Camara B\n9: journal: Eur J Biochem\n10: year: '1998'\n11: doi: 10.1046/j.1432-1327.1998.2510413.x\n12: keywords:\n13: - Amino Acid Sequence\n14: - \"Arabidopsis/genetics, metabolism\"\n15: - Base Sequence\n16: - Cell Compartmentation\n17: - Chlorophyll/metabolism\n18: - \"Cloning, Molecular\"\n19: - Escherichia coli/genetics\n20: - \"Gene Expression Regulation, Plant\"\n21: - Lipids/biosynthesis\n22: - Molecular Sequence Data\n23: - \"Oxidoreductases/genetics, metabolism\"\n24: - Plastids/metabolism\n25: - Polyisoprenyl Phosphates/metabolism\n26: - \"Recombinant Proteins/genetics, metabolism\"\n27: - Sequence Analysis\n28: - Up-Regulation\n29: content_type: abstract_only\n30: ---\n31: \n32: # Metabolic compartmentation of plastid prenyllipid biosynthesis--evidence for the involvement of a multifunctional geranylgeranyl reductase.\n33: **Authors:** Keller Y, Bouvier F, d'Harlingue A, Camara B\n34: **Journal:** Eur J Biochem (1998)\n35: **DOI:** [10.1046/j.1432-1327.1998.2510413.x](https://doi.org/10.1046/j.1432-1327.1998.2510413.x)\n36: \n37: ## Content\n38: \n39: 1. Eur J Biochem. 1998 Jan 15;251(1-2):413-7. doi: \n40: 10.1046/j.1432-1327.1998.2510413.x.\n41: \n42: Metabolic compartmentation of plastid prenyllipid biosynthesis--evidence for the \n43: involvement of a multifunctional geranylgeranyl reductase.\n44: \n45: Keller Y(1), Bouvier F, d'Harlingue A, Camara B.\n46: \n47: Author information:\n48: (1)Institut de Biologie Moléculaire des Plantes du Centre National de la \n49: Recherche Scientifique, Université Louis Pasteur, Strasbourg, France.\n50: \n51: The addition of phytyl side chain to chlorophylls, tocopherols and phylloquinone \n52: is prerequisite to their integration into plastid membranes. We have cloned a \n53: cDNA encoding a pre-geranylgeranyl reductase from Arabidopsis thaliana. The \n54: deduced primary structure predicts a mature size with a molecular mass of 47 kDa \n55: and displays a characteristic dinucleotide binding domain. Geranylgeranyl \n56: reductase expressed in Escherichia coli sequentially catalyzes the reduction of \n57: geranylgeranyl-chlorophyll a into phytyl-chlorophyll a as well as the reduction \n58: of free geranylgeranyl diphosphate into phytyl diphosphate. Due to its \n59: multifunctionality and weak hydrophobicity, we suggest that in plastid the same \n60: geranylgeranyl reductase is recruited into the chlorophyll, the tocopherol and \n61: the phylloquinone pathways. The geranylgeranyl reductase gene is up-regulated \n62: during etioplast to chloroplast and chloroplast to chromoplast development.\n63: \n64: DOI: 10.1046/j.1432-1327.1998.2510413.x\n65: PMID: 9492312 [Indexed for MEDLINE]\n\n(End of file - total 65 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"---\nreference_id: PMID:9492312\ntitle: Metabolic compartmentation of plastid prenyllipid biosynthesis--evidence for the involvement of a multifunctional geranylgeranyl reductase.\nauthors:\n- Keller Y\n- Bouvier F\n- \"d'Harlingue A\"\n- Camara B\njournal: Eur J Biochem\nyear: '1998'\ndoi: 10.1046/j.1432-1327.1998.2510413.x\nkeywords:\n- Amino Acid Sequence\n- \"Arabidopsis/genetics, metabolism\"\n- Base Sequence\n- Cell Compartmentation\n- Chlorophyll/metabolism\n- \"Cloning, Molecular\"\n- Escherichia coli/genetics\n- \"Gene Expression Regulation, Plant\"","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"references_cache/PMID_9492312.md","time":{"start":1778982572807,"end":1778982572821}},"id":"prt_e339fd304001i6ED3c0XX3qFK4","sessionID":"ses_1cc676134ffe2LibXsrsp2MYr0","messageID":"msg_e339fc529001lgPDzcCXewEc9i"}}
