upporting work:\n+- Pre-validation: `make travis_build` passed before edits.\n+- Term search: checked `GO:0045550`, `GO:0102067`, and related obsolete chlorophyll-side-chain reductase terms with `obo-grep.pl`.\n+- Design/pattern review: treated this as a reaction-based MF term; no logical definition changes were needed.\n+- Research: validated `PMID:9492312` and recorded the supporting text in `RESEARCH.md`.\n+- Automated validation: `make travis_build` passed after the edit.\n+\n+Checklist:\n+- [x] PLAN: analyzed issue body and comments; request was clear after follow-up comment\n+- [x] PRE-VALIDATION: ontology validated before edits\n+- [x] RESEARCH: supporting literature checked and summarized in `RESEARCH.md`\n+- [x] TERM-SEARCH: relevant GO terms consulted\n+- [x] DESIGN-PATTERNS: reviewed reaction-term precedent and avoided unnecessary logical edits\n+- [x] EDITS: used checkout/checkin workflow via `terms/GO_0102067.obo`\n+- [x] RELATIONSHIPS: no relationship or axiomatization changes required\n+- [x] SPECIALIZED-EDITS: used reaction guidance; obsoletion deferred as requested\n+- [x] METADATA: added issue tracker item; no `created_by` or `creation_date` changes because this is an existing term\n+- [x] AUTOMATED-VALIDATION: `make travis_build` passed after edits\n+- [x] REFERENCE-VALIDATION: `PMID:9492312` validated and matched the stated substrate scope\n+- [x] CHANGES-COMMITTED: ontology change committed locally\n*** End Patch"},"output":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\nA PR_COMMENTS.md","metadata":{"diff":"Index: /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n===================================================================\n--- /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n+++ /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,12 @@\n+Updated `GO:0102067 geranylgeranyl diphosphate reductase activity` and committed the change locally.\n+\n+Per the issue comments, I did not obsolete 